	" is a video game adaptation of the board game backgammon and one of four launch titles for the Intellivision. It allows for two players to play against each other and for one player to play against the CPU, whose difficulty can be adjusted. It also includes sound effects and music that play when a piece is moved, a die is shaken, or a player wins.
